    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just temporary. it's not like a bad mood or a rough patch. the industry, the people i used to call peers... they don't just look past me, they look through me. it's like the person I was actually ceased to exist. you say i can rediscover myself, but how do you rebuild when the foundation is just dust? there is no version of me that's still respectable. it's just over.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
